      "members": [],
      "paragraphs": [
        "A value/ref-kind asset descriptor (asset-system v2 delta §4). Structurally an Asset, but branded so a catalog classifies its leaf as a deferred `AssetRef<T>` — even when `T` is an object type (e.g. typed JSON), where the plain `T extends object` heuristic would otherwise misread it as a resource. The brand is a phantom (never present at runtime)."
      ],
      "importLine": "import { ValueAsset } from '@codexo/exojs'",
      "sourceLink": null
    },
